                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "\n                              <p>which he would inform me of<del>f</del><lb/> In respect to the\n                                        Letter, you wish<lb/> of me <persName>Mr\n                                                  Middleman's</persName> Letter will<lb/> explain—I\n                                        have some other matter<lb/> to communicate to you which I\n                                        will<lb/> attend to immediately after <add>יידיש</add><lb/>\n                                        in the mean time receive my<lb/> best wishes for your\n                                        happiness<lb/> and believe me to be yours<lb/>\n                                                  sincerely—<persName role=\"author\">Ansel\n                                                  Leo</persName></p>\n                              <p>If you wish to publish <persName>Mr<lb/> Middleman's</persName>\n                                        Letter I must request<lb/> you will do so without extracting<lb/>\n                                        <hi rend=\"underline\">one word</hi> from the original<lb/>\n                                        otherwise neither he nor I wish<lb/> to see it in print</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(8)\">Yours</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(8)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">\n                                                  <hi rend=\"underline\">AL</hi>\n                                        </persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Revd I. Leeser</addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>&amp;c &amp;c &amp;c</p>\n                              "
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3nc5t485/canvas/p2"
                }
              ]
